creator: Cachalot
descriptionHtml:
Luna Diary is designed to help you keep track of your daily thoughts and moods in a safe and supportive space.

Features:

Mood Tracking: With Luna Diary, you can track your moods and emotions easily. Choose from a range of emotions, including happy, sad, and angry, and see how they change over time.

Customization: Make your diary unique with customizable themes, fonts, and colors. We have a range of beautiful backgrounds to choose from, so you can personalize your diary to your heart's content.

Password Protection: Keep your diary entries private and secure with password protection. Set a unique password to ensure your thoughts and emotions stay confidential.

Reminders: We know life can get busy, so Luna Diary lets you set reminders to help you remember to write in your diary. Choose from daily, weekly, or monthly reminders to suit your schedule.

Backup and Sync: Backup your diary entries to the cloud and sync them across all your devices. You'll never lose a precious memory again!

Search: Easily find specific diary entries with our search function. Search by keyword, date, mood, or any other criteria you choose.

Luna Diary is here to support your mental wellbeing by providing a safe and welcoming space to express yourself. Download Luna Diary today and start your personal journaling journey - we're here for you every step of the way!

creator: Cachalot
descriptionHtml:
Express your daily mood as the moon.

■ Monthly New Theme Challenge
- Write 7 diaries in a month, and you can unlock one of the premium themes of the month.
- We hope this will help you develop the habit of daily journaling in the New Year.
- It's okay to fail repeatedly. As long as you don't give up, we'll always support your challenge.

■ New Themes Added Every Month
- Prepare to adorn your home screen with a variety of themes, from moon, stars, flowers to beautiful illustrations.
- Choose the theme that suits your taste and create your own memory space.
- New emotional characters with various concepts like cute cookies are also being added along with the moon.

■ The Moon That Represents Your Day
- By assigning your meanings to the moon's shapes or emojis, you can use it as a diary for various themes.
> If you set it to represent satisfaction, it can be a diet diary.
> If set for gratitude, it becomes a gratitude journal.
> Using cute emotion emojis, it can be a mood diary.
- Many people find psychological comfort by sharing their stories with the moon, especially when stressed, depressed, lonely, in need of comfort, or facing hardships.
- The daily records written on the moon will protect your heart.

■ Growing Landscape of the Heart
- The more you use the diary app, the more flowers and stars you'll see.
- The moon fills up according to the number of diaries written in a month.
- Like the increasing flowers and stars and the filling moon, your heart will also become richer.

■ Glass Cards That Support You
- Self-encouragement is more powerful than any other support.
- Write phrases for yourself on glass cards and use them whenever you feel down.
- The more you use them, the clearer the glass cards become, giving you a little strength to live each day.

■ Monthly Review
- See statistics and the trajectory of the moon filled with your emotions for the diaries written over the month.
- Easily analyze the meanings you've stored, all at a glance in the moon's trajectory.
- The review feature is provided as a basic option, not just for premium users.

■ Convenient Features
- Safely store your secret diary with a lock feature.
- Add multiple photos, videos, and music to your diary entries.
- Add a moon-shaped widget to your home screen to make you want to write diaries every time you see the moon on your wallpaper.
- Sort diaries with hashtags to view only what you want.
- When you're unsure what to write, use our diary templates. Answering template questions makes diary writing easier.
